{"readme":"<h1 class=\"title\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://github.com/mikolalysenko/voxelize\">voxelize</a><div class=\"contrib\"></div></h1>\n<p>Voxelize a triangulated mesh into an <a href=\"https://github.com/mikolalysenko/ndarray\">ndarray</a>.</p>\n<h2 id=\"example\">Example</h2>\n<pre><code class=\"lang-javascript\"><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span class=\"comment line double-slash js\"><span class=\"punctuation definition comment js\"><span>//</span></span><span>Load&#xA0;bunny</span><span>&#xA0;</span></span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span class=\"storage type var js\"><span>var</span></span><span>&#xA0;bunny&#xA0;</span><span class=\"keyword operator assignment js\"><span>=</span></span><span>&#xA0;</span><span class=\"support function js\"><span>require</span></span><span class=\"meta brace round js\"><span>(</span></span><span class=\"string quoted double js\"><span class=\"punctuation definition string begin js\"><span>&quot;</span></span><span>bunny</span><span class=\"punctuation definition string end js\"><span>&quot;</span></span></span><span class=\"meta brace round js\"><span>)</span></span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>&#xA0;</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span class=\"comment line double-slash js\"><span class=\"punctuation definition comment js\"><span>//</span></span><span>Voxelize&#xA0;the&#xA0;mesh</span><span>&#xA0;</span></span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span class=\"storage type var js\"><span>var</span></span><span>&#xA0;result&#xA0;</span><span class=\"keyword operator assignment js\"><span>=</span></span><span>&#xA0;</span><span class=\"support function js\"><span>require</span></span><span class=\"meta brace round js\"><span>(</span></span><span class=\"string quoted double js\"><span class=\"punctuation definition string begin js\"><span>&quot;</span></span><span>voxelize</span><span class=\"punctuation definition string end js\"><span>&quot;</span></span></span><span class=\"meta brace round js\"><span>)</span><span>(</span></span><span class=\"variable other object js\"><span>bunny</span></span><span class=\"meta delimiter property period js\"><span>.</span></span><span class=\"support constant dom js\"><span>cells</span></span><span class=\"meta delimiter object comma js\"><span>,</span></span><span>&#xA0;</span><span class=\"variable other object js\"><span>bunny</span></span><span class=\"meta delimiter property period js\"><span>.</span></span><span class=\"variable other property js\"><span>positions</span></span><span class=\"meta delimiter object comma js\"><span>,</span></span><span>&#xA0;</span><span class=\"constant numeric js\"><span>0.1</span></span><span class=\"meta brace round js\"><span>)</span></span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>&#xA0;</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span class=\"comment line double-slash js\"><span class=\"punctuation definition comment js\"><span>//</span></span><span>Unpack&#xA0;result</span><span>&#xA0;</span></span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span class=\"storage type var js\"><span>var</span></span><span>&#xA0;voxels&#xA0;</span><span class=\"keyword operator assignment js\"><span>=</span></span><span>&#xA0;</span><span class=\"variable other object js\"><span>result</span></span><span class=\"meta delimiter property period js\"><span>.</span></span><span class=\"variable other property js\"><span>voxels</span></span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span class=\"storage type var js\"><span>var</span></span><span>&#xA0;origin&#xA0;</span><span class=\"keyword operator assignment js\"><span>=</span></span><span>&#xA0;</span><span class=\"variable other object js\"><span>result</span></span><span class=\"meta delimiter property period js\"><span>.</span></span><span class=\"variable other property js\"><span>origin</span></span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span class=\"storage type var js\"><span>var</span></span><span>&#xA0;resolution&#xA0;</span><span class=\"keyword operator assignment js\"><span>=</span></span><span>&#xA0;</span><span class=\"variable other object js\"><span>result</span></span><span class=\"meta delimiter property period js\"><span>.</span></span><span class=\"variable other property js\"><span>resolution</span></span></span></div>\n</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"install\">Install</h2>\n<pre><code>npm install voxelize\n</code></pre><h3 id=\"-require-voxelize-cells-positions-resolution-\"><code>require(&quot;voxelize&quot;)(cells, positions[, resolution])</code></h3>\n<p>Voxelizes a triangulated mesh into an ndarray</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>cells</code> are the indexed faces of the mesh</li>\n<li><code>positions</code> are the locations of the vertices in the mesh</li>\n<li><code>resolution</code> is the resolution at which the mesh needs to be voxelized</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Returns</strong> An object with the following properties</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>voxels</code> the binary voxel image of the mesh</li>\n<li><code>origin</code> the coordinate of the bottm left back corner of the voxel array</li>\n<li><code>resolution</code> the resolution of the voxel array</li>\n</ul>\n<p>The real location of a voxel (i,j,k) in the mesh coordinates is given by:</p>\n<pre><code>[ resolution * i + origin[0], resolution * j + origin[1], resolution * k + origin[2] ]\n</code></pre><h2 id=\"credits\">Credits</h2>\n<p>(c) 2013 Mikola Lysenko. MIT License</p>\n"}